    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today. It\u2019s a super reliable pick if you\u2019re looking for a great balance of quality and value. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32000.0,
