      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the iconic S54-powered platform. The 3.2L high-revving straight-six features individual throttle bodies and remains exceptionally linear throughout the power band, having recently undergone a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and valve adjustment. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. The chassis has been proactively maintained with subframe reinforcement and upgraded polyurethane bushings to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain and suspension geometry are dialed-in for performance. This is a turn-key driver's car with the critical rod bearing service already completed.",
